  "title": "Banking: Junior Operations Officer (KYC/Account opening)",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>*Seeking for a Junior Operations Officer with minimum 1 year of experience in Branch Bank operations/documentation or Account Opening experience* </strong></em></p><p><strong>THE COMPANY</strong></p><p>The bank is an established set up and are looking to expand their operations. Currently, there are seeking for an Operations Officer who can help with their Branch Banking Operations.</p><p><strong>JOB RESPONSIBILITIES</strong></p><ul><li>Handle bank’s branch operations</li><li>Input customers’ details into the system</li><li>Ensure complete customers’ (Retail and corporates) KYC inputs/documentation</li><li>Deal with complete documentation for Account opening and closing etc.</li><li>Handle GIRO transactions</li><li>Handle relevant reporting</li><li>Liaise with internal and external stakeholders</li><li>Any other adhoc duties</li></ul><p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Business Studies/Finance/Banking/Economics/Commerce or any other relevant education</li><li>Minimum 1 year of experience in Branch Bank operations/documentation and/or in Account opening </li><li>Approachable, diligent, keen eye for details and has good interpersonal and communication skills</li></ul><p>If you will like to explore this opportunity, please email your resume in Microsoft Word format to marie@resolutehunter.com</p><p>We thank you for your interest and will contact shortlisted candidates for more detailed discussio</p><p>For more job openings, please visit our website at https://resolutehunter.com/opportunities/</p><p>EA Licence 18C910</p><p>EA Reg R1105305</p>",
